                            שנין<lb/>
                  <surplus>שנין</surplus> לחרבן בית מקדש<lb/>יוחז במדבח
                        ויתערר<lb/>לקול משמע ש<supplied reason="lost">לם</supplied>
                  <lb/>שלם<lb/>שלם<lb/>שלם</p>
            </div>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>May there rest the sould of Yehudah the priest, son of Abdi[.]mah, who was
                    gathered (on) the third day of the month Kislev, in the fifth year of the
                    seven-year cycle, which is the year 300 {hundred} (and) 90 years {years} of the
                    destruction of the Sanctuary. May he hold the altar and wake up to the voice of
                    the announcer of peace. Peace, peace, peace.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" ana="b1">
                <p>3 Kislev 390 E.D.S., 5th S.Y. is equivalent to 25 November 458 CE</p>
            </div>
